query: SELECT os.id, os.numeroOs, os.placa, os.status, os.km, os.motivoVisita, os.valorTotalOs, os.createdAt, c.nomeCompleto as cliente FROM ordens_servico os LEFT JOIN clientes c ON os.clienteId = c.id ORDER BY os.id DESC LIMIT 20;
